org.conqat.lib.commons.logging

Interface ILogger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NoOpLogger, SimpleLogger, WrappedLogger

    public interface ILogger
    This interface describes loggers. This interface does not provide methods for logging message at FATAL level as such issues should be signaled with exceptions.
    Author:
    Florian Deissenboeck, Elmar Juergens
